{"word":"ἐπιρρίπτω","slug":"ἐπιρρίπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιρρίπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><i>to cast at</i> another, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>χεῖρα ἐπ.</el> <i>to lay</i> hand <i>upon</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to throw upon</i> one, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><el>ἐπιρριπτέω</el><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>= <el>ἐπιρ-ρίπτω</el>, only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to throw oneself upon</i> the track, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}